Zambian Inflation Accelerates to 9.2% in March, Statistics Agency Reports

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-03-31T09:04:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/zambian-inflation-accelerates-to-9-2-in-march-statistics-agency-reports.html
Zambia’s annual inflation rate rose
to 9.2 percent in March from 9 percent a month earlier on higher
fuel prices, the nation’s Lusaka-based statistics agency said in
a faxed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
